<h3>Active town (work in progress)</h3>
<p>“Active town is a youth exchange project currently in development, which is being prepared and submitted for Erasmus+ funding. Planned to take place in Ypati, Greece, the project aims to engage young people in revitalizing rural communities through alternative tourism, intercultural collaboration, and sustainable local development. Participants will work with local stakeholders, explore the town’s cultural and natural assets, and develop ideas and strategies to strengthen community life and economic opportunities, while encouraging youth participation and promoting rural areas as attractive places to live, work, and invest in.</p>
